Usage: pinAnalysis [-help] [-checkLegality] [-noHtml] [-outFile <string>]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-checkLegality     # Checks the legality of pin assignment (similar to the
                   # checkPinAssignment command) and prints a summary report of
                   # the results. (bool, optional)
-noHtml            # Specifies that HTML report file should not be created.
                   # (bool, optional)
-outFile <string>  # In addition to displaying the report on screen, prints the
                   # report to the specified file. (string, optional)